PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Supply and Services of GERALD IVER NORBRATEN, of Regina, Saskatchewan, as a director of the Board of Directors of Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation from outside the public service of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Ritchie E. Twa, whose term has expired.
